LABEL: 0x12ba

LABEL: 0x1330

LABEL: 0x18a6

LABEL: 0x1a94
ENG: "I mean, there are a lot of weirdos around, too."

LABEL: 0x1af8

LABEL: 0x1b26

LABEL: 0x1c8c

JPN: ひどい言われようだった。

LABEL: 0x240e

LABEL: 0x26ae

LABEL: 0x26e6
